---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="About PowerButter - Our Story" description="Learn about PowerButter's mission to create ultra-premium peanut butter for elite athletes and fitness enthusiasts.">
  <Header />
  
  <main class="pt-16">
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="py-24 bg-gradient-to-br from-neutral-950 via-neutral-900 to-neutral-950">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
          <div>
            <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-display font-bold text-white mb-6 leading-tight">
              Fueling Champions
              <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-accent-400 to-accent-600 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
                Since Day One
              </span>
            </h1>
            <p class="text-xl text-neutral-300 leading-relaxed mb-8">
              PowerButter was born from a simple belief: elite athletes deserve nutrition that matches their dedication. 
              We craft ultra-premium peanut butter that doesn't compromise on quality, taste, or performance.
            </p>
            <div class="space-y-4">
              <div class="flex items-center space-x-3">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-accent-500 rounded-full"></div>
                <span class="text-neutral-300">Founded by professional athletes</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center space-x-3">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-accent-500 rounded-full"></div>
                <span class="text-neutral-300">Trusted by Olympic champions</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center space-x-3">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-accent-500 rounded-full"></div>
                <span class="text-neutral-300">Science-backed formulations</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="relative">
            <div class="aspect-square bg-gradient-to-br from-neutral-700 to-neutral-800 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center">
              <div class="text-neutral-500">
                <svg class="w-32 h-32" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="0.5" d="M4 16l4.586-4.586a2 2 0 012.828 0L16 16m-2-2l1.586-1.586a2 2 0 012.828 0L20 14m-6-6h.01M6 20h12a2 2 0 002-2V6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z"></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Story Section -->
    <section class="py-24 bg-neutral-900">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
          <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-display font-bold text-white mb-8">
            Our Story
          </h2>
          <div class="prose prose-lg prose-invert mx-auto">
            <p class="text-xl text-neutral-300 leading-relaxed mb-8">
              It started in a small garage in 2019. Two professional athletes, frustrated by the lack of truly premium 
              nutrition options, decided to create something different. Something that would fuel not just their bodies, 
              but their ambitions.
            </p>
            <p class="text-lg text-neutral-400 leading-relaxed mb-8">
              After countless hours of research, testing, and refinement, PowerButter was born. We source only the 
              finest peanuts, employ cutting-edge processing techniques, and add performance-enhancing ingredients 
              that actually make a difference. Every jar represents our commitment to excellence.
            </p>
            <p class="text-lg text-neutral-400 leading-relaxed">
              Today, PowerButter is trusted by Olympic athletes, professional sports teams, and fitness enthusiasts 
              who refuse to settle for ordinary. We're not just making peanut butter – we're crafting fuel for champions.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Values Section -->
    <section class="py-24 bg-neutral-950">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-display font-bold text-white mb-4">
            Our Values
          </h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-neutral-400 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
            These principles guide everything we do, from sourcing ingredients to crafting the perfect jar.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
          <div class="bg-neutral-900 rounded-xl p-8 text-center group hover:bg-neutral-800 transition-colors">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-accent-500 to-accent-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Quality First</h3>
            <p class="text-neutral-400">We never compromise on ingredient quality or manufacturing standards.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-neutral-900 rounded-xl p-8 text-center group hover:bg-neutral-800 transition-colors">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-accent-500 to-accent-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19.428 15.428a2 2 0 00-1.022-.547l-2.387-.477a6 6 0 00-3.86.517l-.318.158a6 6 0 01-3.86.517L6.05 15.21a2 2 0 00-1.806.547M8 4h8l-1 1v5.172a2 2 0 00.586 1.414l5 5c1.26 1.26.367 3.414-1.415 3.414H4.828c-1.782 0-2.674-2.154-1.414-3.414l5-5A2 2 0 009 10.172V5L8 4z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Science-Based</h3>
            <p class="text-neutral-400">Every formulation is backed by sports nutrition science and research.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-neutral-900 rounded-xl p-8 text-center group hover:bg-neutral-800 transition-colors">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-accent-500 to-accent-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Sustainability</h3>
            <p class="text-neutral-400">Ethical sourcing and sustainable practices for the planet and future generations.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-neutral-900 rounded-xl p-8 text-center group hover:bg-neutral-800 transition-colors">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-accent-500 to-accent-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Community</h3>
            <p class="text-neutral-400">Supporting athletes and fitness communities worldwide in their journey to excellence.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Team Section -->
    <section class="py-24 bg-neutral-900">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-display font-bold text-white mb-4">
            Meet Our Founders
          </h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-neutral-400 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
            Two athletes who transformed their passion for performance into a mission to fuel champions.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="aspect-square bg-gradient-to-br from-neutral-700 to-neutral-800 rounded-2xl mb-6 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto w-80">
              <div class="text-neutral-500">
                <svg class="w-24 h-24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1" d="M16 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0zM12 14a7 7 0 00-7 7h14a7 7 0 00-7-7z"></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Alex Rodriguez</h3>
            <p class="text-accent-400 font-medium mb-4">Co-Founder & CEO</p>
            <p class="text-neutral-400 leading-relaxed">
              Former Olympic weightlifter with a passion for sports nutrition. Alex brings 15 years of elite athletic 
              experience and a deep understanding of what the body needs to perform at its peak.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="aspect-square bg-gradient-to-br from-neutral-700 to-neutral-800 rounded-2xl mb-6 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto w-80">
              <div class="text-neutral-500">
                <svg class="w-24 h-24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1" d="M16 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0zM12 14a7 7 0 00-7 7h14a7 7 0 00-7-7z"></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Dr. Sarah Chen</h3>
            <p class="text-accent-400 font-medium mb-4">Co-Founder & Head of Innovation</p>
            <p class="text-neutral-400 leading-relaxed">
              Sports nutritionist and food scientist with a PhD in Biochemistry. Sarah leads our research and development 
              efforts, ensuring every product meets the highest standards of performance nutrition.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Stats Section -->
    <section class="py-24 bg-gradient-to-r from-accent-900 via-accent-800 to-accent-900">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-display font-bold text-white mb-4">
            Our Impact
          </h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-accent-100 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
            Numbers that reflect our commitment to excellence and the trust athletes place in us.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-white mb-2">1M+</div>
            <div class="text-accent-100">Athletes Served</div>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-white mb-2">50+</div>
            <div class="text-accent-100">Olympic Medals Won</div>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-white mb-2">100%</div>
            <div class="text-accent-100">Natural Ingredients</div>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-white mb-2">5★</div>
            <div class="text-accent-100">Average Rating</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA Section -->
    <section class="py-24 bg-neutral-950">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center px-6 lg:px-8">
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-display font-bold text-white mb-6">
          Ready to Fuel Your Journey?
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-neutral-400 mb-8">
          Join the thousands of athletes who trust PowerButter to fuel their performance and achieve their goals.
        </p>
        <a 
          href="/products" 
          class="inline-block bg-gradient-to-r from-accent-500 to-accent-600 hover:from-accent-600 hover:to-accent-700 text-white px-12 py-4 rounded-full font-bold text-xl transition-all duration-300 transform hover:scale-105 shadow-2xl"
        >
          Shop Premium Collection
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  
  <Footer />
</Layo>